[01:02.97] Walking my personal Calvary mile to a do-it-yourself crucifixion,
[01:10.52] It's a kingdom of clowns wearing martyrdom's frown -
[01:15.12] I must fight for my hammer and nails,
[01:18.27] We're an endless procession of lost, dispossessed unbelievers -
[01:24.76] Whose prayers go unheard and unanswered,
[01:29.74] (Unheard and unanswered like junk mail for Jesus).